{"tid":2452846,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"漫威漫畫因應同志驕傲月　預計將在6月推出首位同性戀美國隊長","createTime":"2021-03-19T05:40:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-19T11:18:32.000Z","uid":22675,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4347e9d12080353f2f6556390d3d5193e2910dac","tid":2452846,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T05:40:06.000Z","msg":"為了迎接6月「同志驕傲月（Gay Pride Month）」的到來，世界各地也開始準備相關活動來慶祝，而先前DC Comics也如往常一樣，將在2021年6月8日發行內容總80頁的DC Pride，與多達9種的變體封面。<br />\n<br />\n另外，Marvel Comics部分剛好也正逢「美國隊長」80週年慶祝，因此官方也決定將在今年6月推出全新漫畫《The United States Of Captain America》，而這也是Marvel Comics連載以來，首位LGBTQ+美國隊長。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5dobs9C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5dobs9C.jpg&h=de017f55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《The United States Of Captain America》由編劇Christopher Cantwell，以及擔任繪師的Dale Eaglesham共同合作，講述歷任美國隊長&mdash;史蒂夫羅傑斯、巴奇巴恩斯、山姆威爾森，以及約翰 F.沃克四人，共同尋找被偷走的盾牌，並在旅途中遇上了新任美國隊長「亞倫&middot;菲舍爾（暫譯，Aaron Fischer）」。<br />\n<br />\n據Marvel官方設定，這位「新任美國隊長」亞倫&middot;菲舍爾為一名街頭英雄，同時也是一位男同性戀者，他的挺身而出是為了幫助那些無家可歸且流浪在外的人們，他的初登場也將在《The United States Of Captain America》#1中，並由Joshua Trujillo 與Jan Bazaldua負責。"},{"pid":"26daba1a0b0a2dfb74b23def34dacf3c60ee96e3","tid":2452846,"uid":377617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T05:40:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/rubbish.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15e31cac890300b0afdd635c1af5c80b8ef7c510","tid":2452846,"uid":331590,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T05:40:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32eb03564d